claims:
3.如权利要求2所述的一种风光储联合发电系统的有功优化控制系统所应用的控制方法，其特征是，具体工作步骤如下：
		3. The control method applied in the active power optimization control system of a wind-solar-storage combined power generation system as claimed in claim 2, wherein the specific working steps are as follows:



         步骤一：电网根据风功率和光功率预测并结合负荷情况制定出力计划曲线，将出力计划曲线下发给风光储联合发电系统控制中心站，风光储联合发电系统控制中心站根据风电场当前出力、光伏电站当前出力和储能电站当前出力以及风功率和光功率预测制定风电场、光伏电站和储能电站的出力计划；
		Step 1: The power grid formulates an output plan curve based on wind power and optical power forecasts combined with load conditions, and sends the output plan curve to the control center station of the wind-solar-storage combined power generation system. The current output of the power station and the current output of the energy storage power station, as well as the forecast of wind power and optical power, formulate the output plan of the wind farm, photovoltaic power station and energy storage power station;



         步骤二：风电场控制子站和光伏发电控制子站接收风光储联合发电系统控制中心站下发的出力计划，并结合当前控制子站收集得到的有功出力情况，制定各子站的出力调整计划，结合子站内各机组单元的出力状态，制定各机组单元的出力调整计划，并下发给各机组单元；
		Step 2: The wind farm control sub-station and the photovoltaic power generation control sub-station receive the output plan issued by the wind-solar-storage combined power generation system control center station, and combine the active power output collected by the current control sub-station to formulate an output adjustment plan for each sub-station , based on the output status of each unit in the substation, formulate an output adjustment plan for each unit and issue it to each unit;



         步骤三：储能控制子站根据风光储联合发电系统控制中心站下发的发电计划，调整电池组的发电出力大小，同时上传储能控制子站的功率偏差；
		Step 3: The energy storage control sub-station adjusts the power generation output of the battery pack according to the power generation plan issued by the wind-solar-storage combined power generation system control center station, and at the same time uploads the power deviation of the energy storage control sub-station;



         步骤四：风机控制单元接收风电场控制子站下发的出力调整计划，对风机单元进行功率调整，计算功率调整偏差，若功率调整偏差不为零，则反馈调整偏差，将调整偏差上传给风电场控制子站；光伏阵列控制单元接收光伏发电控制子站下发的出力调整计划，对光伏阵列单元进行功率调整，计算功率调整偏差，并反馈调整偏差，将功率偏差上传给光伏发电控制子站；
		Step 4: The wind turbine control unit receives the output adjustment plan issued by the wind farm control substation, adjusts the power of the wind turbine unit, and calculates the power adjustment deviation. If the power adjustment deviation is not zero, it feeds back the adjustment deviation and uploads the adjustment deviation to the wind power plant. Field control sub-station; the photovoltaic array control unit receives the output adjustment plan issued by the photovoltaic power generation control sub-station, adjusts the power of the photovoltaic array unit, calculates the power adjustment deviation, and feeds back the adjustment deviation, and uploads the power deviation to the photovoltaic power generation control sub-station ;



         步骤五：风电场控制子站根据风机控制单元上传的功率调整偏差，结合所有风机控制单元的出力计划执行情况，判断风机控制单元是否达到出力限值，最低限值为零，最高限值为风功率预测得到的最大值；若达到出力限值，将该风机剔除掉本轮次的出力调整计划；对于未达到限值的风机控制单元，形成出力调整计划，将出力计划下发到相应的风机，同时计算风电场控制子站的功率偏差，并上传到风光储联合发电系统控制中心站；光伏发电控制子站根据光伏阵列控制单元上传的功率调整偏差，结合所有光伏阵列控制单元的出力计划执行情况，判断光伏阵列控制单元是否达到出力限值，最低限值为零，最高限值为光功率预测得到的最大值，；若达到出力限值，该光伏阵列剔除掉本轮次的出力调整计划；对于未达到限值的光伏阵列控制单元，形成出力调整计划，将出力计划下发到相应的光伏阵列，同时计算光伏发电控制子站的功率偏差，并上传到风光储联合发电系统控制中心站；
		Step 5: The wind farm control substation judges whether the wind turbine control unit has reached the output limit according to the power adjustment deviation uploaded by the wind turbine control unit and combined with the execution of the output plan of all wind turbine control units. The minimum limit is zero, and the maximum limit is wind power. The maximum value obtained by power prediction; if the output limit is reached, the fan will be removed from the output adjustment plan of this round; for the fan control unit that does not reach the limit, an output adjustment plan will be formed, and the output plan will be issued to the corresponding fan At the same time, calculate the power deviation of the wind farm control sub-station and upload it to the control center station of the wind-solar-storage combined power generation system; the photovoltaic power generation control sub-station adjusts the deviation according to the power uploaded by the photovoltaic array control unit, combined with the output plan of all photovoltaic array control units. If the PV array control unit reaches the output limit value, the minimum limit value is zero, and the maximum limit value is the maximum value obtained from the optical power prediction; if the output limit value is reached, the PV array will eliminate the output adjustment plan of this round ;For the photovoltaic array control unit that has not reached the limit, form an output adjustment plan, send the output plan to the corresponding photovoltaic array, and calculate the power deviation of the photovoltaic power generation control sub-station, and upload it to the control center station of the wind-solar-storage combined power generation system ;



         步骤六：风光储联合发电系统控制中心站根据风电场控制子站、光伏发电控制子站和储能控制子站上传的功率调整偏差形成新的发电出力计划，并下发给控制子站；在此过程中，风电场和光伏电站运行到限值，最小限值为零，最大限值为风功率和光功率预测得到的最大值，或是功率调整偏差为零，则本次调整结束。
		Step 6: The control center station of wind-solar-storage combined power generation system forms a new power generation output plan according to the power adjustment deviation uploaded by the wind farm control sub-station, photovoltaic power generation control sub-station and energy storage control sub-station, and sends it to the control sub-station; During this process, if the wind farm and photovoltaic power station run to the limit, the minimum limit is zero, and the maximum limit is the maximum value obtained from the wind power and optical power prediction, or the power adjustment deviation is zero, then this adjustment ends.
